{"lastModified":null,"uri":"c::22672890147::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThe largest sailing catamaran in our range without a flybridge, the Aura 51 is a real game-changer. She is designed for sailors – with or without a crew – who aspire to experience cruising with a capital C for comfort.\n\nThe Aura 51 marks the entry point into the world of luxury yachting and uninhibited pleasure...\n\nAt 15.54 meters long, it’s easy to see that the Aura 51 catamaran will be generous with space, because she can afford to be. Her hulls have a configuration flexibility that is rare a sailing catamaran of this size, offering the option of not one, but two owner’s cabins that each feature direct access from the stern. Her cockpit-saloon deck layout – which affords breathtaking views and can be completely opened up – is also a first. Featuring the latest in energy management technology, she is equipped with an innovative propulsion system on the ‘Smart Electric’ version.","blueprint":{"name":"ALTHEA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5::assets::0bd71740-f2ea-11f0-8659-e12187d45177/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5::assets::0bdce3a0-f2ea-11f0-865b-e12187d45177/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5::assets::0bdbab20-f2ea-11f0-865b-e12187d45177/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5::assets::0bd31fa0-f2ea-11f0-8659-e12187d45177/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5::assets::0bd4cd50-f2ea-11f0-8659-e12187d45177/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5::assets::0bdeb860-f2ea-11f0-865b-e12187d45177/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::01a262d0-f2e4-11f0-a55a-d5c007b21ce5::assets::0bdbd230-f2ea-11f0-865a-e1